Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} has fallen\N after losing to Malik's Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm begging you! Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that very moment, the\N Millennium Tauk Ishizu gave me\N showed me a vision of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll believe in that future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to keep my promise with Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to obtain the\N future I saw back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Sky Colosseum Duel:\N Yugi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}, we need to start\N the second Duel soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He {\b0}will{\b1} be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless of what happens,\N he can't run away from our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is our fated fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, our fight is waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time to settle this\N has finally come...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your usual annoying peanut gallery\N isn't with you this time, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's coffin must\N be pretty {\i1}heavy{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} is still fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to\N believe whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was facing Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fought that Duel to the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even forced him to pull out God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Duelist, he must be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can at least pass over\N without any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Battle City has been like\N a road of battle for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is our final destination\N when all is said and done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both I... and Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N are still looking for that answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}is{\i0} no "answer" for the fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hang your head low in defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you can stand back up and continue\N searching for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can continue down the\N road of battle until you find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you'll find the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What is a True Duelist?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} is still fighting\N to find that answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, how ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! There's only one true victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who piles up\N the corpses of the defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be able to grasp\N the glory shining in Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was chosen\N by the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I will defeat you and gain\N the title of "Duel King"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did his hand move just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Isn't that helicopter here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go ask Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...\N Yugi's Duel is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm headed to the Duel Ring\N where Kaiba's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you stay here and keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a {\b0}Duelist{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does he insist\N on continuing to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just... can't understand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is\N believe in him and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the light of hope needed\N to disperse the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We swore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as True Duelists...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We still haven't found our answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was worried this Duel would be boring\N because of the damage Jounouchi\N took when he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You haven't lost your fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the second match\N of the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel between Seto Kaiba and\N Yugi Mutou will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or your Osiris!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is now a battle of {\i1}gods{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner of this Duel\N will obtain two God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an ante of pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a battle to determine the\N ultimate Duelists, this site is too drab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have prepared a battle stage\N worthy of our fated Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid Vision System! Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for the title of "Duel King"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be held on the stage of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Duel Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! After countless conflicts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will fight the decisive battle\N in the name of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Ancient Roman gladiators who fought\N with their lives for pride and freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now draw your cards,\N your {\i1}sword{\i0}, from your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my cards are my sword,\N then my Duel Disk is my shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card in my right hand\N is my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Disk in my left hand\N is my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen's Knight!\N In Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The God of Victory always smiles on me,\N regardless of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have to do is put\N three sacrifices on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of strategy\N will Kaiba use in this Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strategy he uses against Ishizu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}destroying the opponent's deck\N with powerful Monsters and spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blood Vorse, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keldo is eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fall into the trap of Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that this Dark Attribute Monster has less than 1000 Attack Points, he becomes the carrier of the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the Monsters on your field and in your deck are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I know the ins and outs\N of his Deck Destruction strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must still have a strategy\N he hasn't used hidden in his deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon X-Head Cannon\N in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Sanctuary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card forces both players to add\N one Magic Card from their deck to their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, this Continuous Magic Card\N allows us to use any Magic Card\N during our opponent's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pick any card you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba... Accepting such high risk\N just to play a Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what Magic Card did you\N get your hands on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a reverse card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're finished next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already have the cards in my hand\N for an Instant Kill Combo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Mokuba! What the hell's \Ngoing on with that helicopter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not looking too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's too much interference in the air\N to reach the control tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!\N That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can anyone hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an injured person here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What was I doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm about to play in the\N District Duel Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my second match is up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you guys watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win this thing for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba and Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clash between the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to see this battle\N with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba's Monster on the field has\N more Attack Points than my Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he didn't attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he being cautious\N of my reverse card?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Summon another Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Warrior Alpha\N in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll also set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll teach you how foolish it is to play\N Low-Level Monsters against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Bow down before God and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll activate a Magic Card\N from my hand on this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross Sacrifice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross Sacrifices makes it so the Monsters\N on your field become my servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I choose to sacrifice them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then sacrifice them along with the\N X-Head Cannon I control,\N totaling three tributes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't do it that easily, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the\N Magic Sanctuary you played,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also permitted to use its\N Continuous Effect that allows me to play\N Magic Cards during my opponent's turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your X-Head Cannon\N becomes {\i1}my{\i0} servant for one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you Summon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw through me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}would{\i0} say that's expected of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you were naïve, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy Controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By entering the right command,\N this card allows me to control one\N of the Monsters on your field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay 1000 of my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left! Right! A! B!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this command,\N I can once again control\N X-Head Cannon as my third sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have three sacrifices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he going to Summon Obelisk\N in just two turns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightforce Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lightforce Sword will keep your\N God Card out of commission for three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will stay sealed away on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too hasty now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's barely gotten {\i1}started{\i0}, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you managed\N to stop an instant kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but your imminent defeat\N has not changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}\N still isn't back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's far too quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Almost like silence before a large storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a battle between\N two owners of the God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Duel is bound to\N become a vicious fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what is going to happen\N the moment it starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Summoning\N of Obelisk was nullified,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three Tribute Monsters\N remain on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cross Sacrifices' effect ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sealed God Card won't return to my hand for another three turns now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have another plan to Summon God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... It's {\i1}your{\i0} turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have two Monsters on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One more and I'll have gathered three sacrifices... enough tributes to Summon my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only... I haven't drawn Osiris from my deck yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-Head Cannon on Kaiba's field has 1800 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't destroy it with the Monsters on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any Monsters with high Attack Power in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just have to sit tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep the Monsters on my field in Defense Mode and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep {\i1}running{\i0} like that, Yugi, your three turns will pass by in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I won't even need three turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to kill you with God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how the Duel's progressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's Obelisk has been pinned by a sealing strategy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi can't attack either...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now which one of them\N will Summon God first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will win this Duel, knowing all that awaits the winner is {\i1}death at my hands{\i0}, deep in the {\i1}darkness{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter {\i1}who{\i0} wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I reserve the right to kill Yugi {\i1}myself{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My next card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Dragon Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon it in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Dragon Head...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba already has X-Head Cannon in his Monster arsenal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X... and Y...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they be Magnet Monsters with the ability to combine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When any two of\N X, Y  and Z are Summoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...their Combination Ability activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now join together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,XY-Dragon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more part...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I play part "Z", they will activate their Ultimate Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With Magnet Monsters, if he can gather all three Union Monsters together, their Attack and Defense Points increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using such a tactic, he can easily destroy my Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then... When the Lightforce Sword stops working,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he can Summon Obelisk by sacrificing the Magnet Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba planned this from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the perfect strategy to Summon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack him, XY-Dragon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyper Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, you weakling Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if he destroys my Defense Monsters, I won't lose any Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... Obelisk has 4000 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I let him Summon it, he'll reduce my Life to 0 in just one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it {\i1}scare{\i0} you that my sealed God\N will be free in just three turns, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I told you I\N {\i1}didn't{\i0} have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gods {\i1}always{\i0} end up\N in the hands of the ultimate Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True {\i1}indeed{\i0}.\N That analysis is right on the mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However{\i0}, {\i1}you{\i0} aren't\N that person, Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate this Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voice of the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card allows me\N to control a High-Level Eight-Star\N Monster or higher residing in your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have the card I name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes... The name of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris the Heaven Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take the God Cad from your\N deck and give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hidden deep\N in your deck, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it doesn't look like you were\N going to draw God during this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kaiba got his hands on\N two God Cards now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gods only obey {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been thinking\N the same thing I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Obelisk\N was freed from hos seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to\N activate this reverse card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hand Exchange Magic Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The trump card I used in my Duel with\N Jounouchi-kun to recover his friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C'mon Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take whichever card you want out of these five cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On that day, we inherited a part of Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s spirit as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And even now, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s\N spirit fights alongside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Kaiba! Time for you to\N return the Osiris card to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mmm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You choose one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi managed to seal the Obelisk card away using the Lightforce Sword's effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he also got the Osiris card back into his hand using Exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he won't be able to Summon his god unless he gets three sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} finally gathers all three Monsters - X, Y and Z - on his field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Yugi manage to Summon Osiris before the effects of Lightforce Sword wares off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Three Knights Used to Call God"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
